This release contains a brand new feature, RemedyMatch. This is a questionnaire designed to evaluate your snoring symptoms, sleeping habits and lifestyle to help find appropriate solutions for your snoring.  There are also the usual bug fixes and performance improvements including: a fix for the "Tell a friend" link, a crash fix when cleaning up audio storage, and a fix for the Rest Rating switch.

Bug fixes, performance improvements and small UI adjustments.

SnoreLab can now integrate with the Apple Watch via the Health app to show blood oxygen saturation and heart rate data alongside your snoring stats! Wear your Apple Watch at night and see vitals charts with our classic snoring chart–a great way to better understand your snoring and sleep health!

This release also contains our new Insights feed tab: a newsfeed of articles related to snoring, sleep and general health as well as in-app achievements and milestones.
